headline: Marsh McLennan’s Mercer Completes Acquisition of SECOR Asset Management
summary: NEW YORK, May 02, 2025--Mercer, a business of Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC) and a global leader in helping clients realize their investment objectives, shape the future of work and enhance health and retirement outcomes for their people, today announced the completion of its previously announced acquisition of SECOR Asset Management. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
